  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/f2bf90a67739bdba0bbb173b796f4ca1.poster.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/f2bf90a67739bdba0bbb173b796f4ca1.webm?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom!</strong> is a trippy arcade platformer ready to take you on a crazy adventure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wait, It's Not A Driving Game?</h2> In this chaotic platformer you spend more time in mid-air than on the ground, even though you have 🚫 <strong>NO JUMP BUTTON!</strong> String together moves to reach spots even the developers haven't accounted for, as you flip, dash and bump your way to new heights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/be42e520c7a5743debb81663a365aaed.poster.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/be42e520c7a5743debb81663a365aaed.webm?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/be42e520c7a5743debb81663a365aaed.mp4?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hoarder's Paradise</h2>We took <strong>\"collectathon\"</strong> seriously! Make your way to the most obscure and difficult to reach corners of our hand-crafted retro levels and we made sure there's something there for you to collect! ... We <strong>dare</strong> you, try to get out of bounds 👀<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d9200f106a1d686aaf205593b55717fc.poster.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d9200f106a1d686aaf205593b55717fc.webm?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d9200f106a1d686aaf205593b55717fc.mp4?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Questionable Crew</h2>Pizza King, Morio and Ultra Chad are only a few of the <strong>weirdos</strong> you'll interact with as you piece together the narrative puzzle and unravel the grand conspiracy happening on Granny's Island! 🌴<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/16cb1a65bd4d602b857946e189cc998e.poster.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/16cb1a65bd4d602b857946e189cc998e.webm?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/16cb1a65bd4d602b857946e189cc998e.mp4?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Genuine Passion Project</h2>This entire project is the brainchild of <strong>Matteo</strong> and <strong>Lorenzo</strong>, who made everything from scratch out of genuine passion for the olden days of video games! 🎮 The game wholly reflects their personality, and judging by the trailer... trust us, it's a trip worth taking!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d4426d5686eabae27ffc4e885edf1a90.poster.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d4426d5686eabae27ffc4e885edf1a90.webm?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/d4426d5686eabae27ffc4e885edf1a90.mp4?t=1744194362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2011780/extras/6aa14cc63dbd10bd2422a784ef2b6c7f.avif?t=1744194362\" width=600 height=152 /></span><br> <br> <br> ",
